title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 286: Featuring Barstool Chief
description:
On Monday’s episode of Spittin’ Chiclets the guys are joined by Barstool Chief. Chief joined (48:01) to talk Blackhawks-Golden Knights, Dylan Strome, Kirby Dach and a bunch more. The boys also talk Tuukka Rask and his decision to leave the bubble to be with his family, a playoff update, some golf and movie talk and a bunch more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
